          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">While this unit is on the battlefield, each of your units gain the following ability:

Tellyporta: After this unit is Activated in reserves, you may use the ‘tellyporta’. If you do, roll 3D6 and Deploy this unit wholly within X” of your TELLYPORTA MEKBOY unit. Then, this unit cannot March or Fall Back this turn.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Dats Be’a" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="2186-1949-d34d-f4f4">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit’s Move step, select a vehicle unit within 3” of this unit or a unit it is embarked within. The selected unit Heals D3+1.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
