          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After a friendly unit with ‘WARBOSS’ in its name within 16” of this unit dies, this unit gains the following ability:


I’m Da Biggest Now: While your infantry units are within 12” of this unit, they gain the following ability:


WAAAAGH!: For each attack that targets this unit, reroll Resilient rolls of 1 for that attack. For each melee attack this unit makes, reroll a Wound Roll of 1 for that attack.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
