        <profile name="Suicidal Acceleration" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="1a64-041d-2832-44ea">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">During this unit’s Move step, instead of making a March move, you may use ‘Warp Tunnel’. If you do, select any point on the battlefield and draw a straight line between this unit and the selected point. Then, this unit suffers XD3 SW where X is the number of different units or terrain pieces along that line and removes this unit from the battlefield and places it into reserves. Then, Deploy this unit within 1” of the selected point.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
