          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit’s End step, if this unit is within 8” of the centre point of a vault, roll 1D6. Either this unit or the unit embarked in it may gain the relic from your relics table which matches the result. If it does, any other of your units with that relic lose it. If the selected unit already has a relic, it loses that relic.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
    </selectionEntry>
